# Collection Name

Brief description of the publication — what it is, who published it, and what kind of content it contains.

## Details

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| **Source** | [Archive Name](https://source-url) |
| **Period** | Month YYYY – Month YYYY |
| **Publications** | N issues / books |
| **Pages** | N |
| **Local PDFs** | `collections/NAME/pdfs/` |
| **Indexed** | `collections/NAME/indexed/` |

## Slug format

Describe the slug pattern used for this collection (e.g. `YYYY-MM` for monthly magazines,
`vol-N` for volumes, `BP-NNN` for numbered books).

```text
indexed/
├── YYYY-MM/
├── ...
└── YYYY-MM/
```

## Coverage notes

- Note any gaps, missing issues, or OCR quality variations.
- Note any special filename patterns or filters applied during download.

## Content character

Describe the typical content: topics covered, project types, target audience, and anything useful
for search and research.
